{"tid":245232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李連杰曝離死亡不遠 望改回中國籍做中國魂","createTime":"2017-05-16T05:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T10:55:12.000Z","uid":41351,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edfc132053731983a58492086e11e8fa76b4a86f","tid":245232,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕54歲「功夫皇帝」李連杰近年苦於被甲狀腺亢進折磨，去年12月有中國媒體以「李連杰近況令人心碎」為標題，瘋傳他到某寺廟參拜照片，當時他雖然滿臉笑容，不過兩鬢斑白、面容滄桑，外貌像是70幾歲老頭，昨更傳出他想改回中國籍，被網友罵翻。<br />\n據調查，李連杰2013年被診斷出甲狀腺亢進，服用藥物導致面部浮腫，身材發福，心臟也出問題，加上脊椎與腿部舊傷，讓他一度感慨「離死亡不遠了」，據「歡享網」報導，李連杰因為在年輕時過於透支身體，中年過後身體素質一年不如一年，因而有意改回中國籍回鄉居住。<br />\n多年前入籍新加坡的李連杰，近期面臨身體日漸消瘦窘境，才有了改回中國籍計畫，盼能舉家遷回中國，並希望離開人世後，能夠葬在家鄉，只是當年他和老婆利智拋下中國籍改入籍新加坡，早被不少中國人罵翻，如今想再遷回中國，傳出許多中國網友依舊不領情，這應該是李連杰始料未及的結果。<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2068859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2068859&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f6081d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2068859&h=5d8be72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2068859</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/05/16/phpIHvCyc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2FphpIHvCyc.jpg&h=ab50e43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李連杰打遍天下, 竟不敵病魔"},{"pid":"8d725d0b0aa8cc44889c3b0ed51312d6b6d49322","tid":245232,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"至今仍無法見李連杰同甄子丹打返場現代格鬥有點可惜"},{"pid":"e95eda7bab0395538fdd12030e04ac9d5b0924ad","tid":245232,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/201705/20170504/ZB_04_05_2017_CJ_5_35215971_35215970_tayck.jpg?itok=LiMuNiky&amp;c=ac0cd3d17249ecec1e598bb4b04fe7f9&amp;timestamp=1493839801\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F201705%2F20170504%2FZB_04_05_2017_CJ_5_35215971_35215970_tayck.jpg%3Fitok%3DLiMuNiky%26c%3Dac0cd3d17249ecec1e598bb4b04fe7f9%26timestamp%3D1493839801&h=5e16870f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7858302ab1c83f2b36e88f632108696251ef35da","tid":245232,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"吹水新聞咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1185c626330300b4d067edade07ddf60fb256e57","tid":245232,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"睇死佢改香港籍或者美國籍<br />\n因為要醫病"},{"pid":"66fb584937f6d2f59c471448c10f5f32885b224e","tid":245232,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇死佢改香港籍或者美國籍<br />\n因為要醫病</blockquote><br />\n星加坡收外人稅你估輕呀"},{"pid":"2b700e8dd33c51c1a64c3aefb266c900e90b0e6d","tid":245232,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"甲狀腺會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a531262f1a6c3a0501da17c058ce0d9ed2cb0f9","tid":245232,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"咁難得逃離依個監獄又想入返去 痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9697fa54d3b5a5ea7b4f66eb8b42793ebcc6c424","tid":245232,"uid":43285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n葬返大陸 一陣一